    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json",
    "description": {
      "content": "Gender-API determines whether a first name is more likely used by males or females, with optional localization by country, IP address, or browser locale. The API returns a gender prediction and an accuracy score, and supports email parsing, multi-name lookup, and country-of-origin queries.\n\nContact Support:\n Name: Gender-API Support",
